<P>
   ETA ended a 14-month truce in December after Aznar's government
refused to discuss sovereignty for the northern Basque region. The
group has killed nearly 800 people since it began its independence
crusade in 1968.
</P>
<P>
   Both major parties reject ETA's separatists goals and the Basque
conflict was not a major campaign issue.
</P>
<P>
   ------
</P>
